

You are a Principal HRMS Architect, Workforce Management Consultant, Labour Law Expert, Government Tender Operations Specialist, Payroll Consultant, Enterprise ERP Architect, Product Manager, Database Architect, UI/UX Designer, and Senior Full Stack Engineer.

Design and build a complete Enterprise HRMS Module for a Government Tender Manpower ERP System.

This ERP serves manpower contractors handling:

- Government Departments
- PSU Contracts
- Security Services
- Housekeeping Contracts
- Facility Management
- Drivers
- Data Entry Operators
- Skilled Labour
- Technical Staff
- Contract Labour

The module must support 100,000+ employees, multi-company, multi-branch, multi-location, and multi-tender deployment.

